    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it sounds like you're saying the policy is flawed. if you had to look at the actual economic arguments, some people say these hikes are basically just a way to force inflation or kill local competition. is there actually any solid economic evidence that these laws work long-term, or is it mostly just based on political pressure?",
